Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What could be\Nbetter than a day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,to gorge on chicken and cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:05.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYou've been acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.61,Main,,0,0,0,,And I want to know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You are amazing in\Nevery way, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would anybody put\Na cat in a swimming pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[DAUGHTER 10A] Look at that\Ntree, Mommy! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[MOTHER 10A]\NIt sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:56.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it would\Nnever get here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:58.62,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's finally the season!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The season of astronomically\Nhigh heating bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That wasn't really\Nwhat I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:08.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It has gotten\Npretty cold, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I could barely bring\Nmyself to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,from under the\Ncovers this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That gives me an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I'll wrap myself in\Nblankets when I'm home
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,instead of turning up the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:19.85,Main,,0,0,0,,That should save a lot of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's one way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] If you let me\Nbuy you a heater,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,then you'll never be cold again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 10A]\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,what I was trying to\Nsay before was that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Christmas is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess it is\Nthat season, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Christmas is\Nvery important, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What could be better than a day\Nto gorge on chicken and cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not actually\Nwhat Christmas is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Wha--? If it's not\Nabout stuffing your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,then why does everyone do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess these days it is mostly\Nabout chicken and cake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Hey, whaddaya\Nthink about throwing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:59.60,Main,,0,0,0,,our very own Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds like\Na fantastic idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.06,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need a lot of\Nchicken and a lot of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] It takes more than\Nchicken and cake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,to throw a good party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,A Christmas party. Fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYoko, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll walk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Did Hayama go to\Nschool early today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently she had some class\Nrep duties to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She sure is busy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,All that sucking up she does...\NIt takes a lot of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I've been thinking\Nabout the Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I decided that I'm\Ngonna bake the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Great! Sounds perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:38.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWe'll have it at your place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,and Hayama will be\Nin charge of snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Did I just overhear you girls\Ntalking about Christmas plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The three of us\Ndecided to have a little party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:59.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I have some information\Nyou might be interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The 25th is a big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not just Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It's also my sister's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO, FUTABA]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up with you two?\NYou're acting kinda funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[overlapping chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:41.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I can't believe\Nthat Hayama's birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.70,Main,,0,0,0,,is on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWait, so that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:51.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs evilly]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] A demon was\Nborn on a holy day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NSuch a contradictory occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[overlapping chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] What are you\Neven talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYou've been acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,And I want to know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWe have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Earlier, Yoko said there's\Nsomething she needed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,to discuss with me\Nand nobody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't say\Nanything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NSure ya did. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Wait, will you at least\Ntell me where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to get a grip or she's\Ngonna know that something's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,She's really suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think we should do\Nabout the Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll still have a party,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,only now it'll be a\Nbirthday party for Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Huh?\NHow will that work, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll keep planning, and\Nwhenever we talk to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll act like it's for\Nthe Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Think how surprised she'll\Nbe when she finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,it's actually for her birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So we're going to set\Na trap and ambush her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Not really how I'd put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,The important thing to remember\Nis to keep it a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,from Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't breathe\Na word to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from,\Nand what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I'm passing out flyers\Nfor Christmas cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I thought I told you not\Nto do that here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Are you sure?\NThat's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If our sales were to go up,\NI might be able
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,to afford to give you a raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse to be tempted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You and your flyers\Nwill leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Cake shops must be\Nbusy this time of year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.01,Main,,0,0,0,,what with all the parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,We have been\Nworking quite hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of normal business,\Nthere are orders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,for specialty cakes\Nand holiday pastries,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,so we've been baking nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, "we"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you mean you actually\Nhelp with the baking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I measure out ingredients\Nand sprinkle things on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,She is an expert sprinkler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I would\Nsurvive the busy holiday season
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.45,Main,,0,0,0,,without her assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You look so shocked,\Nbut as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,my help is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You are amazing in\Nevery way, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,So, we done with\Nthis conversation yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.92,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're so vital\Nto the cake shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,does that mean you'll have\Nto work on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I give you permission\Nto take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:07.34,Main,,0,0,0,,After a life of loneliness,\Nyou finally have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I will work from dawn\Nuntil dusk without rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,so you may celebrate\Nyour friend's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Despite her lack\Nof experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,she's somehow\Nslightly more useful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,than a cat in a swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll make me blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay, seriously.\NCan we be done now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHold on just one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would anybody put\Na cat in a swimming pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, we didn't see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I want to know\Nwhat the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.50,Main,,0,0,0,,have to say that I'm\Nnot allowed to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I must confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We have been keeping\Na secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, Sonobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth is I'm planning to\Nadd bear and cat-shaped cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,to the shop menu\Nsometime in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, YOKO]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I asked the others\Nto keep it a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,because I wanted\Nto surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Aww! I'm sorry\NI spoiled the surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:56.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,That maid's more\Nuseful than she looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,We owe Sonobe for\Ngetting us out of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI love Christmastime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,The streets are so pretty,\Nand people look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And it's so much fun\Nto pick out presents!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I wonder which\None would look better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Pink's nice, but the red\None's really pretty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I spent an hour\Ndeciding and wound up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.30,Main,,0,0,0,,getting both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It cost my whole allowance,\Nbut I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.97,Main,,0,0,0,,My sweet Eternal\Nis worth twice that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Things are really starting\Nto come together, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I'm very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never had the chance\Nto throw a birthday party
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,for a friend before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] We have to make sure\Nit's the best party ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Since it's Christmas and\NHayama's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat's up, Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that about just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You were saying something\Nabout Hayama's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOh, you heard that, did ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We were talking about\NHayama's birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.92,Main,,0,0,0,,and the fact that it\Nfalls on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,We're throwing her a party,\Nbut it's a surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.79,Main,,0,0,0,,so don't say anything\Nabout it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:07.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWe appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 10A]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you tell him that I\Nwant a bike and a video game...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NNo, that's too crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO humming "Jingle Bells"]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NNishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you sitting\Ndown there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Best day of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I know how much you\Nlike Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,so I thought that\Nthis year, maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NIt's not special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Just another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You're always so happy\Nthis time of year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe a Christmas party\Nwill cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NNo, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'll just get\Nsome take-out instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe a nice curry or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyour problem is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.14,Main,,0,0,0,,but you and I are having\Na Christmas party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Now come on, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop being such a grump and\Nlet's go pick out a cake
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,for our party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I'm taking off!\NSee you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You are gonna love this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I spent all night making this\Nspecial stew for your party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NSpecial, or scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] I hope you three\Nhave fun tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't decide. Where do\Nyou think should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Anywhere, just pick a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She's gonna be here\Nany minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey, I'm here!\N--[FUTABA] Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!\NAnd happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I really thought you\Nwere gonna shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You're mean sometimes, but\Nwe wouldn't shoot you for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess my sister\Nmust have told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't mention it\N'cause I didn't want you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,to feel obligated\Nto do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt's not about obligation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI usually just celebrate it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,along with Christmas anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'm used to my\Nbirthday being secondary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,That's kinda sad, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.03,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been years since\NI've had a birthday party
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.66,Main,,0,0,0,,with more than just family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Want some cake?\NI baked it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds yummy, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I helped out by\Nmeasuring ingredients
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,and sprinkling things on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Well it looks\Nexpertly sprinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot, I brought\Nsomething with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,My sister made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let food go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't know\Nthat it is food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:08.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO gagging]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, maybe you should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYou can do it, Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, how amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I almost feel like I could\Nrun a marathon right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Should we call a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I guess I\Nshouldn't have brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NUgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NYa know, at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,you're gonna have\Nto let this go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like some sort\Nof cruel joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,How can Christmas be my\Nfavorite day of the year
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,if it's her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Was your Christmas\Nfestive and full of joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NGo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You know it's also the day I was\Nbrought into the world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to apologize to\NChristmas right this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see why\NI should do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,When the streets are\Ndecorated so prettily
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.66,Main,,0,0,0,,to celebrate my advent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You're horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a nasty,\Nevil Christmas-ruiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate you so much,\NHayama! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughs]\NPeace on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEELZEBUB meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEELZEBUB meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I can't believe how\Nmuch has piled up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only the first\Nsnow of the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:41.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NYeah, it is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I find the feel of\Nfreshly fallen snow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,to be invigorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:49.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Invigorating or not,\Nwe can't open the shop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,until it's all cleared away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO sighs]\NI suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It's freezing out here.\NAnd my back's starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NMiss Yoko is too delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,She shouldn't be\Nforced to shovel snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:07.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet this is your fault!\NYou made it snow, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] You've accused me\Nof a lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,but that's a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt doesn't seem to be stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Won't we be slow?\NI can't imagine that many people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,will want to come out\Nin this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThat's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:24.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a known fact that many\Npeople love blizzards
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.57,Main,,0,0,0,,and will be more eager than\Nnormal to venture out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NReally? I've never heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm surprised even\Nyou came on a day like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:36.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I was lookin' outside\Nat the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,and it gave me the\Nstrongest craving for cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] So, something with\Nwhipped cream for you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NTiramisu, chocolate ganache,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,and opera cake please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Were you looking at snow\Nor at the mud puddles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,left behind after\Nit's melted away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHey, Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's snowing like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But we can't let a\Nbeautiful blanket of snow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,go to waste, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The best way to spend\Na cold, snowy day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.62,Main,,0,0,0,,is inside with a warm,\Nsnuggly cat on your lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:08.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NOh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Just for a little,\NI promise! It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NNo! I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEELZEBUB meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:20.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] Ta-da!\NCheck out the igloo I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Were you out here\Nall night or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NIsn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.55,Main,,0,0,0,,And it's even warm inside, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on, see what it's like!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get us\Nsomething hot to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She wasn't lying.\NIt is warm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHow strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knew that snow could\Nhold in so much warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NUh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[phone chimes]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like Hayama got buried\Nin some kind of avalanche!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA shivering]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when\Nyou go outside on a snow day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NTeru, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanna come out and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Teru, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanna come out and... play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Just checkin' in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:25.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I got a message saying\Nthat you were in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] There's this\Nthing called a doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I can't believe\Nit still hasn't stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's gonna\Nsnow the rest of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So what are you\Ndoing for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Any big plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know if\NI'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] You mean you're\Ngonna be spending it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable!\NI will not allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I don't have\Nanyone to spend it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just an idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,but why don't the three\Nof you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:56.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThat is, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.52,Main,,0,0,0,,assuming that Hayama and\NFutaba would be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:16:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You can count me in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.94,Main,,0,0,0,,New Year's is more fun if\Nyou spend it with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you both so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.82,Main,,0,0,0,,With that decided, I suggest\Nyou have a pajama party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NBut what's... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Something that girls do.\NSimilar to a rite of passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.95,Main,,0,0,0,,A recent study on the\Nprevalence of pajama parties
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:21.50,Main,,0,0,0,,revealed that more\Nthan 80% of all girls
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,will have attended\Nat least one by the time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.09,Main,,0,0,0,,they graduate high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you just made that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But perhaps you're\Nintimidated by the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,of hosting such an\Nimportant gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Nothing intimidates\Na Nishikawa daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I will host a pajama party, and\NI will do it in grand fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that all right with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds a good time to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Then we will need\Ndecorations, hor d'oeuvres,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,and of course a tiered cake\Nto mark the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, pajama parties tend\Nto be a little more relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We basically just\Nhang out in bed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,wearing pj's and\Ntalk about stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not like any kind\Nof party I've ever heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWe need a lot of blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think you have\Nenough at your place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,or should we bring some\Nwith us when we come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, blankets...?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,We all have blankets.\NWhat are we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.08,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the part\Nwhere we're supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,to talk about being\Nin love and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.80,Main,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I love rice and bread too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Carbs are the best!\NI could eat them forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I love cats, and dogs too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't choose between them!\NPlease don't make me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NSo this is a pajama party?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I almost forgot.\NI brought snacks for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! I shall make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That looked painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[overlapping chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,This is completely unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.55,Main,,0,0,0,,A real pajama party\Nshould involve a lot more
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,girlish squealing and giggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You orchestrated this.\NWhat are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not up to\Nanything, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I simply want Miss Yoko\Nto have the experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,any normal girl her age does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:42.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you recording it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,To preserve the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NDeranged old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NCreepy stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NWell, at least she won't spend
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,her New Year's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, I can hardly believe\Nit's already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not just morning.\NIt's a whole new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year\Nto you as well, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I would say our pajama\Nparty was a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.25,Main,,0,0,0,,A total success!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[chopping noise]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Food's almost ready\Nfor ya, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Anything\Nfor you, my sweetcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, get ready to\Npound some mochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.60,Main,,0,0,0,,To do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NNo idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a mochi pounding machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,When you said\N"pounding mochi,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:23.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I was imagining a mortar\Nand pestle type situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Cool, huh? I asked\Nfor it for my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, YOKO]\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:33.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And now to eat! Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,High school girls enjoying\Na post pajama party
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,breakfast of mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What an extremely rare\Nand beautiful sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] What have I told\Nyou about recording them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NIt's for preservation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I'm in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's delicious,\Nand so fresh, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:56.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:57.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Pan-fried with\Nsoy sauce and served
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:21:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,with your choice\Nof edamame paste,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.78,Main,,0,0,0,,fermented soy bean\Npaste, or walnuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,How many dozens should I make?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?\N--Did you just say "dozens"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Mochi's the most important\Npart of New Year's!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on ladies, enjoy yourselves,\Ngo wild, try one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,This is breakfast, not one\Nof your big-eater challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:16.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[overlapping chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NStop it! No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.18,0:23:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NAn event in February?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:51.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That must be--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI] Yes, the\NFestival of Broken Needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,An event where\Na memorial service
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.06,Main,,0,0,0,,is held for broken needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It's an event geared\Ntowards women.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.31,0:23:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NValenti--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NOr the Bean Throwing Festival!
